{
  "name": "Borders",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>Borders</strong> 属性可返回包含所有四个边框的 <strong>Borders</strong> 集合。 可以对单元格或区域的每一侧应用不同的边框。 有关如何对单元格区域应用边框的详细信息，请参阅 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Borders\">Range.Borders</a></strong> 属性。</p>\n<p>只能对 <strong>Range</strong> 和 <strong>Style</strong> 对象的各个边框分别设置边框属性。 其他带边框的对象（如误差线和序列线）具有被视为单个实体的边框，而不管它有多少边。 对于这些对象，在返回边框和设置边框属性时必须将其作为一个整体处理。 有关详细信息，请参阅 <strong>Border</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向第一张工作表上的单元格 A1 添加双边框。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineStyle</span> = xlDouble\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>使用 <strong>Borders</strong> (索引) （其中 index 标识边框）返回单个 <strong>Border</strong> 对象。 Index 可以是以下 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlBordersIndex 枚举.html\">XlBordersIndex</a></strong> 常量之一： <strong>xlDiagonalDown</strong> 、 <strong>xlDiagonalUp</strong> 、 <strong>xlEdgeBottom</strong> 、 <strong>xlEdgeLeft</strong> 、 <strong>xlEdgeRight</strong> 、 <strong>xlEdgeTop</strong> 、 <strong>xlInsideHorizontal</strong> 或 <strong>xlInsideVertical</strong> 。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表 Sheet1 中单元格区域 A1:G1 的底部边框颜色设置为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:G1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlEdgeBottom).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在区域中的所有单元格周围生成一个细边框。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> borders = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B6:D8&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>\n    borders.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineStyle</span> = xlContinuous\n    borders.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> = xlThin\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例更改区域的内部单元格边框。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> borders = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B2:D4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>\n    borders.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlInsideHorizontal).<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineStyle</span> = xlContinuous\n    borders.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlInsideHorizontal).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> = xlThin\n    borders.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlInsideVertical).<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineStyle</span> = xlContinuous\n    borders.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlInsideVertical).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> = xlThin\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>由四个 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Border/Border .htm#Border.Border\">Border</a>**对象组成的集合，它们分别代表 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a>**或 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Style/Style .htm#Style.Style\">Style</a>**对象的四个边框。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a>**对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个代表指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a>**对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Color",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>对象</th>\n<th>对应颜色</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>Border</strong></td>\n<td>边框的颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Borders</strong></td>\n<td>一个区域的所有四条边的颜色。如果四边不是同一种颜色，则 <strong>Color</strong> 返回的是 0（零）。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Font</strong></td>\n<td>字体的颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Interior</strong></td>\n<td>单元格底纹的颜色或图形对象的填充颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Tab</strong></td>\n<td>选项卡的颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置对象的主要颜色，如注释部分中的表格所示。<strong>Variant</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置 A2 单元格的边框颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表的 C4 单元格的边框颜色是否为纯红色*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> == <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ColorIndex",
      "summary": "<p>如果全部四条边框不是同一种颜色，此属性返回 <strong>Null</strong>。</p>\n<p>颜色可指定为当前调色板中颜色的索引值，也可指定为下列 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlColorIndex 枚举.html\">XlColorIndex</a></strong> 常量之一：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>xlColorIndexAutomatic</strong></li>\n<li><strong>xlColorIndexNone</strong></li>\n</ul>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Variant</strong> 值，它代表全部四条边框的颜色。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 A2 单元格的边框颜色是否为无颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> == xlColorIndexNone)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一个工作表中 E3 单元格的边框颜色设置为黄色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">6</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表集合中对象的数量。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿的第一个样式对象的边框数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Styles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "LineStyle",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置边框的线型。<strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlLineStyle 枚举.html\">XlLineStyle</a></strong>、<strong>xlGray25</strong>、<strong>xlGray50</strong>、<strong>xlGray75</strong> 或 <strong>xlAutomatic</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例为 Chart1 的图表区和绘图区域设置边框。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chart = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>)\n    chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineStyle</span> = xlDashDot\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> border = chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PlotArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>\n    border.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineStyle</span> = xlDashDotDot\n    border.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> = xlThick\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将选定区域的所有边框线样式设置为实线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineStyle</span> = xlContinuous\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "ThemeColor",
      "summary": "<p>如果对象当前未应用主题颜色，试图访问其主题颜色则会引起无效请求运行时错误。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置已应用的配色方案中的主题颜色，该配色方案与指定对象相关联。可读/写 <strong>Variant</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 A2 单元格的主题颜色设置为指定“强调文字颜色6”主题颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = msoThemeColorAccent6\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 E10 单元格的主题颜色是否为指定无主题颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> == msoNotThemeColor)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "TintAndShade",
      "summary": "<p>可以为 <strong>TintAndShade</strong> 属性输入 -1（最暗）到 1（最亮）之间的数字，零 (0) 为中间值。</p>\n<p>如果将此属性设置为小于 -1 或大于 1 的值，则会引起运行时错误：“指定的值超出了范围”。此属性用于主题颜色和非主题颜色。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Single</strong>，使颜色变深或变浅。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 I1 单元格边框的 TintAndShade 设置为0.5。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 E6 单元格的 TintAndShade 值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E6&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Value",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>等价于<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Borders/Borders .htm#Borders.LineStyle\">Borders.LineStyle</a></p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿的第一个样式对象的边框线设置成 xlContinuous 。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Styles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = xlContinuous\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿的第一个样式对象的边框线条样式是否为 xlNone 。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Styles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == xlNone)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Weight",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 **<a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlBorderWeight 枚举.html\">XlBorderWeight</a>**值，它代表边框的粗细。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 E6 单元格边框的粗细设置为 xlThick 。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E6&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> = xlThick\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 D3 单元格边框的粗细是否为 xlThin 。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> == xlThin)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
